<div class="page-width" style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 4rem auto; padding: 0 2rem;">
  <h1 class="h1 text-center" style="color: var(--color-gold); margin-bottom: 1rem;">The Wolfpack Channel</h1>
  <p class="text-center" style="color: #999; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
    Strategies for the Infinite Game. Fuel for the Hustle.
  </p>

  <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 4rem;">
    <a
      href="https://www.youtube.com/@BuildYourWolfpack?sub_confirmation=1"
      target="_blank"
      class="btn"
      style="padding: 1rem 3rem; background: #c4302b; color: #fff; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block;"
    >
      Subscribe on YouTube
